# The receiver is authored on any OS but runs on Android, Debian and Raspberry
# Pi OS. A CRLF line ending in a shell script makes bash fail with the
# famously unhelpful "\r: command not found", and a CRLF in a systemd unit is
# silently ignored. Pin them to LF regardless of the developer's platform or
# core.autocrlf setting.

* text=auto eol=lf

*.sh        text eol=lf
*.service   text eol=lf
.env.example text eol=lf

*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.ico binary
